{"tid":1626797,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】火箭總經理撐港言論惹議　環時：不能吃中國還罵中國","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:07.000Z","uid":193217,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bae572b9b80dcd6a01cd385cf3e44d5d408e2936","tid":1626797,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GEEtRui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGEEtRui.jpg&h=ff2241bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國NBA球隊侯斯頓火箭的總經理莫利（Daryl Morey，內地稱莫雷）周六（５日）在Twitter上載一張寫有「Fight For Freedom」、「Stand With Hong Kong」標語圖片，表態支持香港近期的社會運動。惟此舉引起大量內地網民不滿和憤怒，「莫雷支持港獨」亦隨即成為微博熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n同日，內地官媒《環球時報》旗下的《環球網》轉載中國籃球評述員楊毅的微博貼文，指侯斯頓火箭「17年來從中國獲得的贊助商不可計數」，因此「不能吃中國還罵中國」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d3a170b39f0e61f4e5448f5fc7e6a6acffa6b9","tid":1626797,"uid":193217,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"人地話支持香港自由.幾撚時屌柒你大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以你同班生番講野真係無用<br />\n落後我地至少30年後上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad99f8400d98a8c7b16db8584bce398b768305f","tid":1626797,"uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"香港人除了到海外留學, 在香港本土接受的全部是英國殖民地教育, 由小到大學習的都與中國有很大的差別, 所謂的差別是價值觀不同, 不同的是香港人學習了無論在日常生活中的自律, 公德, 衞生; 教育上的文化, 通識; 社會上的法治, 公義, 人權等等, 與中國(中華人民共和國)的價值觀都非常不同(亦即是所謂的文化差異), 香港人和中國人自小從各自地方受教育, 文化差異不同大家都很清楚。香港為英國殖民地超過100年, 100年呢個數目遠超過中國(從當時只有48年建國的時間), 中國人要喺香港要求香港人習慣超過100年嘅生活模式後火速變成一個中國人思維? 完全是極不可能, 香港人會明白你哋中國人的思想, 但當你哋唔明日香港人思想之前加予施壓、不公、荒謬絕倫嘅政府政策, 甚至打壓人權及言論自由, 還未計算香港本土居民長久建立起來的福利於短短不到10年已經令人怒髮衝冠。請你尊重一下香港人, 亦等於尊重自己。"},{"pid":"1ebb9b94d40ac2ffed6d3cba9047027a11440d8e","tid":1626797,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"大陸人以為nba真係因為佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957db565d21f0bff67d91b859db5b50dd27577ad","tid":1626797,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">上載一張寫有「Fight For Freedom」、「Stand With Hong Kong」標語圖片</span><br />\nDel左post? 搵唔到"},{"pid":"c27dd4639f24c3d7d734b447584fc36dedff98e2","tid":1626797,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9831e00ac06e673aab2b046b6cc31508db4d1b","tid":1626797,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"On9 jai"},{"pid":"7ea6bc8f500a60298c21dfd30b2fb28b0d1814e0","tid":1626797,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957db565d21f0bff67d91b859db5b50dd27577ad","tid":1626797,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">上載一張寫有「Fight For Freedom」、「Stand With Hong Kong」標語圖片</span><br />\nDel左post? 搵唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:17.000Z","msg":"受壓力del左"},{"pid":"f75111ec4ba105b70793b87d49311efedc73a13d","tid":1626797,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:23.00